### Get all users

GET http://localhost:3000/api/users HTTP/1.1


### GET a single user
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/leon9000 HTTP/1.1

### GET a single user which doesn't exist
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/peter HTTP/1.1

### Delete a user
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/users/hendrik246 HTTP/1.1


### POST a user
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Bob",
    "username": "bob123456",
    "password": "srorginsoin"
}